message.en_US: Hi?
That's a relief, we're here.
This is an abandoned area west of the main playground.
It used to be the \c[3]player housing\c[0] of a player who is no longer active.
He was a notorious hacker who was \c[1]banned\c[0] from Crossworlds long ago.
Thus his account was deleted and this place has fallen into disrepair.
However there is still something in that building that we can use to better protect you.
Can you head inside?
[nods]
It's locked?
[nods]
There should be a switch to open it around here somewhere.
Why don't you take a look around?

task.en_US: Find the \c[3]switches\c[0] to unlock the door to the \c[3]abandoned compound\c[0].

message.en_US: It looks like parts of the ground have collapsed.\. Mind your step.
Careful!\. We're lucky the respawn mechanism still works all the way out here.
Please try to avoid falling in the pits.
...You really like jumping in the pits, don't you?
Lea, please stop jumping in the pits.
There will be plenty of time for that once we reach the main playground.
Wow, where did you learn to jump like that?
And on the \c[3]first try\c[0] too!
I'm not sure what I expected for an answer.
Nice find!\. That looks like one of the switches to open the door.
There should be \c[3]2\c[0] more in the area.
The player who originally lived here evaded the moderators for years.
He used a special \c[1]hacking device\c[0] which created a false identity to trick the Crossworlds servers.
Well done!\. Please head inside.
